description:
BEYOND the DARKNESS finds Reality Denied: Firsthand Experiences with Things that Can't Happen - But Did with John B. Alexander Ph.D.

JOHN B. ALEXANDER, Ph.D., is a retired senior Army officer with decades of experience with a wide range of phenomena. Traveling to all eight continents, he has encountered events that defy common explanation. Tonight we begin our journey with him to Skinwalker Ranch and the unnerving case of UFO & Chris Bledsoe.

Get his book here: Amazon.com/shop/darknessradio
